@base = http://localhost:3001

### ── CORE ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Site settings (global)
GET {{base}}/api/globals/site-settings?locale=vi

### Pages
GET {{base}}/api/pages?locale=vi&limit=10

### Posts
GET {{base}}/api/posts?locale=vi&limit=9&sort=-publishedAt

### ── BIOSCOPE ────────────────────────────────────────────
### Ingredients (supplements) with relationships
GET {{base}}/api/ingredients?where[type][equals]=supplement&depth=2&locale=vi

### Ingredients (featured)
GET {{base}}/api/ingredients?where[featured][equals]=true&depth=1&locale=vi

### Technologies sorted
GET {{base}}/api/technologies?sort=order&depth=2&locale=vi

### Services
GET {{base}}/api/services?sort=order&locale=vi

### Certifications
GET {{base}}/api/certifications?sort=order&locale=vi

### Partners
GET {{base}}/api/partners

### ── GRAPHQL ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/api/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{ "query": "{ Ingredients(locale: vi, limit: 3) { docs { id name slug type } } }" }

### ── B2B ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Register (creates a pending member)
POST {{base}}/api/b2b/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "new@acme.com", "password": "Member@123", "company": "ACME", "contactName": "Tester", "phone": "0900000001" }

### Login (approved seeded member) — sets payload-token cookie
# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/b2b/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "member@acme.com", "password": "Member@123" }

### Current member
GET {{base}}/api/b2b/me

### Documents the member may access
GET {{base}}/api/b2b/documents

### Logout
POST {{base}}/api/b2b/logout
